items.title: Apple offers modest growth outlook after iPhone sales help beat profit expectations
items.description: Earnings per share were 97 cents including the charge related to a one-time multi-billion-euro European tax payment.

items.title: Investor that had a 3,700% return on Tencent sets sights on India
items.description: The new chief executive officer and former startup founder has begun scouring the globe to replicate the blockbuster success from Prosus’s $34 million deal in 2001 to buy 50% of China’s Tencent Holdings Ltd
